snippet.title: In Sound Mind Release Date Trailer - Future Games Show GamesCom 2021
snippet.description: In Sound Mind is a psychological thriller with original music from The Living Tombstone. We Create Stuff's horror puzzler is coming to PlayStation, Xbox and PC on September 28, with a Nintendo Switch version coming later in 2021.
